    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but did it actually change much for people on the ground? feels like some people say the legislation didn't really fix the underlying issues or that the nonviolent stuff wasn't as effective as others argue. what's the consensus on whether it actually achieved its full potential?",
